          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">
          "I just graduated with a Mathematics and CS degree but felt unprepared for the real world. The mentorship helped me build practical projects, understand industry best practices, and nail my interviews. I got my dream remote job at a tech company within 6 months!"
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">
            S
          </div>
          <div class="ml-3">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Sodiq Onawale</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Recent Math & CS Graduate → Fullstack Developer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

